Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:52.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}希望の風が{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.23,0:00:56.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}はじけそうな　情熱を{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}運んで來るよ{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}もし茝くなら{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.51,0:01:05.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}つげたい きみに{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.89,0:01:09.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}告げたい君に{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}I'm not strong but{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:15.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}My wind is high{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}一人じゃないと思える{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}明日をそこに感じる{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.51,0:01:39.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}信じるカがあせてないから{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.59,0:01:43.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}胸に舞い上がる{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}予感の風が{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.81,0:01:50.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}また飛べそうな ときめきが{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}埞ってくるよ{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.70,0:01:57.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}あの大空を{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.04,0:02:00.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}あげたい君に{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.45,0:02:04.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}今どこまでも　行けそうさ{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}I'm not strong but{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}My wind is high{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.70,0:02:52.90,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\bord0\3c&Hf0ffff&\c&Hf0ffff&\pos(538.125,487.5)\shad0\fs62.5\fscx110\fad(1000,0)}在阳光普照之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.79,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}2017年世界冠军新条直辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}经过多年的奋斗终于获得了冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}再次送上热烈的掌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨!雪铁车队的海尼尔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 你不恭喜我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.89,0:03:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼 拿不到冠军恭喜不恭喜也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欧洲站的第一位是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.99,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以雪铁的实力当然能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.09,0:03:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么同样是这辆赛车\N某个人怎么拿不到冠军呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 是因为你的驾车技术有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.69,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,简单的说就是你没有技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没技术 没技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 他很有实力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个已经是迟来的冠军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.89,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说今后是他的时代也不夸张呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧  新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你发什么呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.79,0:04:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在想为你的冠军送什么礼物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我什么也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.39,0:04:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是如果是她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫她做AOI车队的主机械师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.89,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀 好丰盛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是颁奖盛宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 加贺先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他竟然在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次是代替领队来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人他也应该好多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样不行啊 加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你该立即来找我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为AOI车队的首席车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有很多人等着你去打招呼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首席车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.69,0:05:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺决定在下一个赛季加入我们车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 的确是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论如何下届比赛我们都是最强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来和相关人物打个招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不知道吗 新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 老板从来不太提这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 恭喜你 世界冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没对你说过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都是托明日香的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没...没什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.89,0:06:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊...你在电话里跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吓了一跳吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你现在才16岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为你年纪还小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不是马上结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.79,0:06:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不过担心明日香会被人抢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.69,0:06:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论隼人退出车坛后选择什么路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.49,0:06:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管发生什么事我们永远都会在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,订婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恭喜你 明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀  对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了  隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝你们幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.39,0:07:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你爸爸也会默默祝福你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧  太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.99,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊  真想不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.29,0:07:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了没精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也应该恭喜他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您是认真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你对隼人有什么不满吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人活泼而且也有决心有毅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是个很好的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑了  我反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们太年轻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以说还是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.39,0:07:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且隼人你对赛车有什么打算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽说连续两年夺冠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你绝对可以做得更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是你作为车手的黄金时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得这个时候该订婚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥连一次世界冠军都没有拿过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且隼人他不再参赛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些事情已经与他无关了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥你也别再优柔寡断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快点和克蕾雅小姐订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心她被别人抢走了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿修他很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.19,0:08:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,英国也好  德国也好  西班牙也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都有女朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.59,0:08:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说年轻人就该广交朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克蕾雅怎么在这时候说这些事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是  那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是订婚还真不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想订婚了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就订婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克蕾雅小姐你除了哥哥外还有其他的人选吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.89,0:09:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.29,0:09:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿修你说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们两个的确还太年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.29,0:09:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是他们自己决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就为他们祝福吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.89,0:09:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不是反对他们订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,双方的父亲是从小的玩伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也认为这事迟早要发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是现在的他仅仅是在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是也没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人他曾经...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,徘徊在死亡的边缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.99,0:10:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也曾经历过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做车手的谁没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的心情我能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.89,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,普通车手要花十多年才能到达的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是隼人出道三年间就到达了顶峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.39,0:10:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以他的才华还有许多潜力没被挖掘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论做任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.39,0:10:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经验都是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而他只是经过三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但决定那些事情的不是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是隼人自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿修也说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.39,0:10:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人几乎触及了人类极限的领域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是指零的领域吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.39,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人受的伤有多深我们外人是看不出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不打算让他放弃比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.89,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他们两人正互相扶持 一同向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.79,0:11:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们向他们祝福不是更好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也应该继续向前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,率领没有隼人的菅生车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要回到赛车场上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了  隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.69,0:13:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很累吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不  没有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗  我总觉得你没有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像不太开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.39,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起  最近睡得不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.79,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}第十三届高智能方程式揭幕站 巴西锦标赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.09,0:13:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}决赛还有几分钟就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.99,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}今天备受关注的是菅生车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}15岁的新人的安尼·古力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧  隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.99,0:14:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}他有出色的驾驶技术和新车花环的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.79,0:14:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}我们能否看到菅生车队创造奇迹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}还有上届胜出的AOI车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.09,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}已经三年没有参赛的布利德加贺复出参赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}还有天才卡尔·里胥特·冯·兰德尔的近况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}都令我们期待....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香  等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要生气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你始终忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛车的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你刚才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因为修哥也出场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才留意了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仅仅如此而已 真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个东西很像你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜欢的话我送给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌  我不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.19,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是如果你想要买东西给我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个很可爱的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.89,0:15:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.49,0:15:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,订婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊  你说要给我买的不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你该挑个更象样点的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶  我就要这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我晚点再买更好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那东西做订婚戒指会被人笑话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,值不值钱没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我最重要的订婚戒指啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是只属于隼人和我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.19,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们和佣人说过以后自作主张在这里等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底去了哪里？我等了两个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又没有通知我 不要生气嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事先也应该打个电话来阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然有时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为我除了现在还有时间来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还是个独断独行的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但真是好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身体还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.09,0:16:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.69,0:16:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是就在前些日子内心又遭受了重创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说你和隼人订婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日本的日落也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.49,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出去走走吧  隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没有消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.99,0:17:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒也有点喜欢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我原本有点像女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样看来多少也有点男子气概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是妈妈看起来很生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.49,0:17:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借着受伤的事吵吵嚷嚷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人  这伤痕不关你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啰嗦  不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我退出了赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你现在做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.49,0:18:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给爸爸帮忙做生意在世界各地飞来飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.09,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且在没有你的跑道上比赛也挺无聊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.09,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道我迟早也会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.99,0:18:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我对现在的生活没有什么不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.79,0:18:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再伟大的人也总有无能为力的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我来说最开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许就是和你在赛道上较量的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么也不能代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了  我没有时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十分开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我时常想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.09,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么时候能在跑道上再和你较量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天我姑且祝福你们的订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果和隼人吵架的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.99,0:19:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上和我联络哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是贺礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在旅行社出示它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以得到飞往世界各地兰德尔集团别墅的飞机票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.69,0:19:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么...再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.99,0:19:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那张卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以用它和隼人去蜜月旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁要去那家伙的别墅度蜜月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是这样才像兰德尔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这儿待多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大约三天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天还有些简单的测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今年有些不对劲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴西站是第四位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美国站是第六位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老板都开始不耐烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟发生了什么事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.69,0:20:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了  我也没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是...什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跑道上已经没有舒马赫也没有隼人和兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一想到这里就没法集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你可以去超越其他车手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.09,0:21:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那城之内你现在怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吗...继续做机械的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菅生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你没有去赛场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.69,0:21:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可惜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.99,0:21:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以你的能力在菅生实在是大材小用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有很多车队向我招手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.39,0:21:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也包括你的车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.19,0:21:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.09,0:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的车队条件远远比菅生....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论是待遇或者各方面都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且可以和你工作也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也这么想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我还在等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.79,0:21:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果...如果隼人回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还希望和他一起在菅生工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.59,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且阿斯拉达也有几个型号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上个赛季他突然退出我仍有些不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.79,0:22:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.49,0:22:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或者隼人比我更能体现你的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.29,0:22:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.59,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他一出道就连拿两届冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.79,0:22:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见和我相比...你更想跟随他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.69,0:22:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么...新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了...不要介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.39,0:22:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人  怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.69,0:23:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.89,0:23:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人  不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.29,0:23:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不小心弄倒的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.79,0:23:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上收拾你不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.19,0:23:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.79,0:23:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.59,0:23:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有玻璃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.69,0:23:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我不知道怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.09,0:23:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.19,0:23:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我又做那个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.99,0:23:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.39,0:23:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.49,0:23:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事的 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.89,0:23:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很快就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.39,0:23:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.59,0:24:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又做那个梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.89,0:24:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在安慰隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.49,0:24:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你回房间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.39,0:24:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再说了快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算和明日香订婚来逃避恶梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但似乎没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.39,0:24:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.79,0:24:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的人生的确是属于你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.19,0:24:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是隼人你想逃避到什么时候呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.09,0:24:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.29,0:24:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你和明日香都会受不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.79,0:24:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人你真的想担惊受怕地过一辈子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.59,0:24:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.59,0:24:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底要我怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.59,0:24:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你自己应该知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.99,0:25:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我来说最开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.79,0:25:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许就是和你在赛道上较量的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.09,0:25:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想什么时候能在跑道上再和你较量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.09,0:26:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.80,0:26:32.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&H0000FFFF}[ Ending Theme ]{\c}{\c&He0ffff&} Get up!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.26,0:26:41.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}目指す夢　ある限り{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.35,0:26:44.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}人はみな強くなる{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.48,0:26:50.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}敗れても立ち上がる　何度も{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.72,0:26:53.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}輝きの真ん中で{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.84,0:26:56.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}傷ついて知ってゆく{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.88,0:27:01.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}大切なものがあるね{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.55,0:27:09.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}無力な今に泣いていたって{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.66,0:27:15.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}一途に欲しい明日が{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.00,0:27:21.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}I'll get victory! victory! I will be winner!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.21,0:27:27.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}I'll get victory! victory! もう 一度{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.48,0:27:33.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}I'll get victory! victory! I will be the champ!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.74,0:27:39.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}新しい挑战が始まる{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.21,0:27:43.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&He0ffff&}Get up!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.10,0:27:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.40,0:28:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:01.10,0:28:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香不可以吵架啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.80,0:28:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那么野蛮隼人要被你吓跑了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.70,0:28:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我一开始就反对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.80,0:28:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年轻人应该广结良缘谨慎地把握未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.40,0:28:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你终于要回归车队了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.80,0:28:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.20,0:28:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在菅生车队的位置不保哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.00,0:28:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新世纪GPX CYBER FORMULA ZERO第三集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.30,0:28:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重返赛车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.20,0:28:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在零的领域内等着你
